Date: Sun, 28 Oct 2018 23:29:41 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] nvme: free cmbuf in nvme_exit
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This avoid a memory leak in unhotplug nvme device.

Signed-off-by: Li Qiang <liq3ea@gmail.com>
Reviewed-by: Philippe Mathieu-Daud√© <philmd@redhat.com>
Signed-off-by: Kevin Wolf <kwolf@redhat.com>
diff --git a/hw/block/nvme.c b/hw/block/nvme.c
index 36bf4d4bea..5199f24aee 100644
--- a/hw/block/nvme.c
+++ b/hw/block/nvme.c
@@ -1058,6 +1058,9 @@ static void nvme_exit(PCIDevice *pci_dev)
     g_free(n->cq);
     g_free(n->sq);
 
+    if (n->cmb_size_mb) {
+        g_free(n->cmbuf);
+    }
     msix_uninit_exclusive_bar(pci_dev);
 }
 
